                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 20437/96.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">American Ambassador</gloss> to the
                            <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Berlin</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1910-06-06">
                            <hi rend="italic">June 6, 1910</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Answering your June 1. Apparently impossible to procure repeal of potash law,
                    passed with full knowledge of our views. I suggest immediate request for most
                    favorable conditions obtainable from Bundesrat under section 46.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hill.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
